<item>
            <title>[SPARK-1052] Spark on Mesos with CDH4.5.0 cannot start the Tasks properly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-1052</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Steps :&lt;br/&gt;
Start the mesos cluster with the deb 0.15 from mesosphere.&lt;br/&gt;
Install cdh 4.5.0.&lt;br/&gt;
Start the spark-shell with this code :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;val data = 1 to 10000&lt;br/&gt;
val distData = sc.parallelize(data)&lt;br/&gt;
distData.filter(_&amp;lt; 10).collect()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The tasks die because of an exception.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It used to work with Spark 0.8.0&lt;/p&gt;</description>
